### Oxide Plugins by KillParadise
Welcome to the official site page for my plugin collections, here you can see the prototype builds in action, check out the latest code, check out my latest snippets and tutorials, and even get the latest and greatest releases that are not on oxide just yet. Thanks for visiting! I hope you find what you're looking for!
